### GET / -> 200
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en"><head><meta charset="utf-8"><title>Tycho</title></head>
<body>
<nav><a href="/">Home</a> &middot; <a href="/blog">Blog</a> &middot; <a href="/wiki/getting-started">Wiki</a></nav>
<main>
<h1>Tycho</h1>
<p>Tycho is a small systems language with <strong>value semantics</strong> and an <strong>implicit
arena</strong> memory model — no garbage collector, no manual <code>free</code>, and memory that's
competitive with C.</p>
<ul>
<li>Read the <a href="/blog">blog</a> for notes and benchmarks.</li>
<li>Browse the <a href="/wiki/getting-started">wiki</a> to get started.</li>
</ul>
<blockquote>
<p>This whole site is served by a web server <em>written in Tycho</em>, rendering
Markdown through <code>core:markdown</code>.</p>
</blockquote>
</main>
<footer>Served by Tycho.</footer>
</body></html>

